<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.4.10">
<l>kāciṉvāykkaram viṟkiluṅkara vātumāṟṟili cōṟiṭṭu</l>
<l>tēcavārttaipa ṭaikkumvaṇkaiyi ṉārkaḷvāḻtiruk kōṭṭiyūr</l>
<l>kēcavāpuru ṭō ttamākiḷar cōtiyāykuṟa ḷāveṉṟu</l>
<l>pēcuvāraṭi yārkaḷentammai viṟkavumpeṟu vārkaḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In Tirukkōṭṭiyūr dwell those of generous hands</l>
<l rend="indent">who receive words of praise,</l>
<l rend="indent">giving rice without trade or concealment</l>
<l rend="indent">even though a hand[ful] could be sold for gold.</l>
<l>Those who say “Keśava!”, “Puruṣottama!”, “Shining Light!”, “Dwarf!”,</l>
<l rend="indent">are servants who get to sell us.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
